    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this extraordinary specimen, preserved in impeccable showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and free from any cosmetic or mechanical imperfections, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. For the discerning buyer seeking an uncompromising automotive investment, this unit offers a rare combination of prestige and performance.",
