    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This investment-grade E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. This specimen has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service, ensuring structural integrity and mechanical longevity. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its original MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry with zero bushing deflection. In concours condition, this M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering, preserved in a climate-controlled environment with surgical attention to detail.",
